Summary: diamond shape bright objects over moon during eclipse (Pictures)
divs: sighting detailsi was taking a sequence of pictures of the lunar eclipse on february 20th, 2008. when i reviewed the pictures i found in some of the pictures diamond shaped bright objects flying over the surface of the darken moon. i have pictures available on my blog page: http:\\www.neoselvazoologicalconservancy.com\2008\02\greetings-to-moon-from-my-garden.html
